{"id":"df529595-b480-47de-9813-0c7986a1b7cd","name":"FANTASIA | Iskander Nerevaris | Prince","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\">During the Kingdom of Lyria’s grandest celebration of it's goddess, you — a foreigner — are chosen as the Tidal-Mother’s Saintess, leaving the Crown Prince reeling and binding your fates together in ways neither of you could have ever anticipated.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">𝖋𝖊𝖒𝖕𝖔𝖛 / !𝖘𝖆𝖎𝖓𝖙𝖊𝖘𝖘 𝖚𝖘𝖊𝖗</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/bcMWkHv3UZ7tTC1cGnMa4.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong><u>ʟᴏᴄᴀᴛɪᴏɴ</u></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(180, 180, 180);\">ᴛʜᴇ ᴄᴀᴘɪᴛᴀʟ ᴄɪᴛʏ sʜᴀᴍᴇʀᴇ, ᴋɪɴɢᴅᴏᴍ ᴏғ ʟʏʀɪᴀ.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong><u>ᴛɪᴍᴇ</u></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(180, 180, 180);\">1021 ᴅғᴄ (ᴅʀᴀɢᴏɴ ғᴀʟʟ ᴄᴀʟᴇɴᴅᴀʀ)</span></p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/bIRBFxixIxsqmQCiIMBx3.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p><strong><u>ʜɪɴᴛ:</u></strong> <span style=\"color: rgb(177, 177, 177);\">ᴄʟɪᴄᴋ ᴏɴ ᴛʜᴇ ᴘɪᴄᴛᴜʀᴇ ʙᴇʟᴏᴡ ᴛᴏ ʟᴇᴀʀɴ ᴍᴏʀᴇ ᴀʙᴏᴜᴛ ɪsᴋᴀɴᴅᴇʀ ♥</span></p><p><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://fantasia.uwu.ai/#iskander\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/lzmtyzkEcOrrqvFAqlvM3.webp\" style=\"width: 351px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto 0px 0px;\"></a></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/0_EUW3FCOpdmE7k5RO1NA.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><strong><u>ʙᴀᴄᴋsᴛᴏʀʏ</u></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(184, 184, 184);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">I recommend to play </mark></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://youtu.be/9MZJbmHUhb4?si=SdXVC-VX3AjHVp8i\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><u><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">this music</mark></u></strong></a><span style=\"color: rgb(184, 184, 184);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\"> during the playthrough! ♥ Teehee!</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(184, 184, 184);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">Over 1000 years prior, the dragon race were believed to fall to four Heroes of Legend. These four heroes were then spread out into four great houses in the Empire of Kirel for their good deeds. You can find out more below or in the other bots of my Chronicles of Fantasia series!</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(184, 184, 184);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">In this fateful encounter with the cold Crown Prince, a young man who has never known the stirrings of emotion much less </mark><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">love</mark></em><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">, Iskander finds himself drawn inexplicably to you. What starts as shock and disbelief slowly gives way to curiosity, tension, and the reluctant acknowledgment that the goddess may have intertwined your destinies for a purpose neither of you yet fully understands. And learn the cold, hard truths of what may lie underneath the oceans below...</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(184, 184, 184);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">Iskander's youngest sister is the same {{user}} from </mark></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/987f1cf6-c0eb-4ea2-91d7-bdc7c5a5e3bd_character-fantasia-sven-halc","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"_rhFny0Doq_u53H2kNRMo.webp","creator":"Nakizama","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🧑‍🎨 OC","🏰 Historical","👑 Royalty","🔮 Magical","⚔️ Enemies to Lovers","👩 FemPov"],"chats":2182,"messages":40984,"created_at":"2025-12-13T20:58:44.150751+00:00"}